lyrics:
You're so delicious
You're so soft
Sweet on the tip of my tongue
You taste like sunlight

Own me, you own me
You rattle my bones

'Till I can't control myself
Make me a liar
One big disaster
But you make my heart beat faster

It's the way you swell, slow
Pushing right out your seams
It's the way you smile, baby
When you've got me on my knees

Your all night noise
Your siren's howl
You make my heart beat faster

Own me, you own me 
You rattle my bones
You turn me over and over 
And I can't control myself
Make me a liar
One big disaster
'Cause you make my heart beat faster

Cause I jump, I crash, I crawl
I beg, I steal, I stalk
Yeah you own me
And you make my heart beat faster

(I can't get enough
Because its on like 
I guess this world is over to me)

You own me, you own
You rattle my bones
You turn me over and over 
'Till I can't control myself
Make me a liar
